00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:45.980
=A Vow in the Dark=

00:00:46.390 --> 00:00:47.370
Lady Serpent

00:00:47.370 --> 00:00:48.820
=Episode 7=
is a beautiful serpent

00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:50.130
who cultivated into an immortal.

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:52.110
When the other realms were unsettled,

00:00:52.390 --> 00:00:53.280
people here

00:00:53.430 --> 00:00:54.790
lived in a constant haze.

00:00:55.030 --> 00:00:56.320
Thanks to Lady Serpent Immortal

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.880
for granting us the divine elixir.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:00:59.350
Once we took it,

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:00.600
we restored appetite

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:02.000
and gained great strength.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:03.880
But Lady Serpent

00:01:04.310 --> 00:01:05.200
was fond of Ji Ling.

00:01:05.790 --> 00:01:06.710
So we volunteered

00:01:06.870 --> 00:01:08.350
to offer a man as tribute

00:01:08.350 --> 00:01:09.920
to pray for a smooth year.

00:01:10.310 --> 00:01:11.870
In the past, those sent there

00:01:11.870 --> 00:01:13.350
would serve with joy and devotion.

00:01:13.950 --> 00:01:14.790
After all,

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.120
Lady Serpent is a peerless beauty.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:18.480
- A peerless beauty?
- Also,

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:19.870
there's glory and wealth to enjoy.

00:01:20.590 --> 00:01:24.590
But word is Ji Ling caused chaos
this time.

00:01:24.790 --> 00:01:27.150
And now, he's vanished without a trace.

00:01:27.950 --> 00:01:28.790
As a result,

00:01:29.150 --> 00:01:30.870
Lady Serpent has been enraged.

00:01:31.710 --> 00:01:34.480
Truly, that's reckless beyond reason.

00:01:34.790 --> 00:01:37.560
Lady Serpent Immortal
descends to the Mortal Realm.

00:01:37.790 --> 00:01:39.620
Everyone, make way.

00:01:40.070 --> 00:01:41.350
Lady Serpent Immortal

00:01:41.350 --> 00:01:42.920
bestows grace upon the world

00:01:42.930 --> 00:01:44.200
at the Zi Hour.

00:01:44.430 --> 00:01:46.120
Ji Ling shall be chosen anew.

00:01:58.790 --> 00:01:59.950
I understand.

00:02:00.230 --> 00:02:02.790
The one who refused to cooperate
was my master.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.640
Don't go, stay a while.

00:02:08.190 --> 00:02:09.400
If not for my master,

00:02:09.400 --> 00:02:11.000
let's at least behold a rare beauty.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.680
(Ji Li and Lady Serpent Immortal)

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.680
(look exactly alike.)

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:30.280
(What in the world is going on?)

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.560
(There must be something unusual here.)

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:45.430
She... I...

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:47.470
A beauty beyond compare?

00:03:49.150 --> 00:03:50.280
She is unpleasant to look at.

00:03:50.590 --> 00:03:51.800
You're barely acceptable.

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:55.960
Wait for me.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:00.920
Ji Li.

00:04:06.700 --> 00:04:11.100
(Serpent Immortal Temple)

00:04:11.470 --> 00:04:14.470
Lady Serpent shields Hunling City.

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:16.600
Yet Ji Ling acted without sense

00:04:16.600 --> 00:04:18.430
and recklessly damaged the palace,

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:19.940
offending the gods above,

00:04:19.950 --> 00:04:21.070
and stirring wrath below.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.340
Lady Serpent nearly withdrew her shield.

00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:26.110
Yet she won't hold the innocent accountable.

00:04:26.380 --> 00:04:28.630
As long as ten Ji Ling are elected anew,

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:30.390
no charges will be pressed.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:37.600
Ji Li, the Serpent Immortal?

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:39.630
What scheme is that traitor up to now?

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:41.630
I'm heading into the Wilds

00:04:41.630 --> 00:04:42.800
to visit the deity.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:45.000
You will make the selection.

00:04:45.270 --> 00:04:46.120
Understood.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.870
Three days from now,

00:04:48.870 --> 00:04:51.360
the first round of the selection
is at the Hot Spring Pavilion.

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.390
Ten taels per person.

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:53.600
Register here with me.

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.390
We bid the Lady Serpent farewell.

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:01.210
The Wilds is a place

00:05:01.210 --> 00:05:03.190
shunned by immortals and demons.

00:05:05.190 --> 00:05:07.560
Ji Li, what are you going there for?

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:12.580
(The Wilds)

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.370
How could the Serpent Immortal

00:05:55.370 --> 00:05:56.630
look exactly the same as me?

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:59.430
I'm just a fish my master raised.

00:06:00.870 --> 00:06:03.390
Could it be
he secretly raised other fish too?

00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:05.720
No, I have to find ask directly.

00:06:05.950 --> 00:06:06.790
Oh.

00:06:08.830 --> 00:06:10.600
That Serpent Immortal looks formidable.

00:06:10.600 --> 00:06:12.040
Even my master was captured.

00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:14.830
I'm barely three hundred years old.

00:06:14.830 --> 00:06:16.160
Such a prime age.

00:06:16.310 --> 00:06:17.190
If I go there now,

00:06:17.190 --> 00:06:18.920
I won't even leave a trace.

00:06:19.390 --> 00:06:20.750
Your Grace, I'll only be able to

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:23.560
plant your spiritual plants in the next life.

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.240
Mm.

00:06:29.390 --> 00:06:31.800
Those chosen as Ji Ling
for the Serpent Immortal

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:32.720
are all as dignified,

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:33.680
peerless,

00:06:33.830 --> 00:06:34.720
and captivating

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.600
as you.

00:06:39.070 --> 00:06:39.910
I'm not going.

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:41.950
I won't rescue Hong Zhua.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:43.680
You'd better drop that idea.

00:06:49.070 --> 00:06:49.910
Miss.

00:06:50.270 --> 00:06:53.160
Would you like to behold
the Lady Serpent?

00:06:53.430 --> 00:06:56.360
Wish to rise above all in Hunling City?

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:58.680
All chosen as Ji Ling
are the finest talents.

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:01.830
Our hall's top ten young gentlemen

00:07:01.830 --> 00:07:03.190
are yours to choose.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.560
Ah, miss.

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:05.400
Look at this one.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:08.310
Thick brows, bright eyes.

00:07:08.310 --> 00:07:09.870
The very figure of elegance.

00:07:09.870 --> 00:07:12.480
He only costs 188 taels of gold.

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.720
He'll be selected as Ji Ling.

00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:15.270
He is impressive.

00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:17.360
But I don't have that much money.

00:07:18.430 --> 00:07:19.950
No problem at all.

00:07:19.950 --> 00:07:22.800
This selection values all equally.

00:07:22.950 --> 00:07:23.920
Look at this one.

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:25.000
Hardworking, resilient,

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:26.190
strong, and sturdy.

00:07:28.070 --> 00:07:29.040
Well, will that work?

00:07:29.630 --> 00:07:31.050
Miss, you're missing the point here.

00:07:31.050 --> 00:07:31.930
Listen,

00:07:31.940 --> 00:07:34.190
this is a rare treasure to be held.

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:40.600
Miss, miss.

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:42.200
Alright.

00:07:45.300 --> 00:07:46.190
Look.

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:47.830
This is my prized collection.

00:07:48.270 --> 00:07:49.190
This young one

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:51.270
comes from a truly pitiful background.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:52.720
He has

00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:54.270
a gravely ill mother, a father

00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:55.510
with a gambling habit,

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:58.430
and a little sister who needs schooling.

00:07:58.870 --> 00:08:00.600
Life pushed him into society.

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:02.000
With no other choice,

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.600
he entrusted this painting to my shop.

00:08:05.390 --> 00:08:06.510
Give him a chance.

00:08:07.310 --> 00:08:08.920
The portrait is strikingly beautiful.

00:08:09.270 --> 00:08:11.310
The price… we can discuss.

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:13.720
This is truly tragic.

00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:16.190
I must do what little I can to help.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.070
May I meet in person?

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:19.360
Of course.

00:08:21.950 --> 00:08:22.790
Why bother meeting?

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:51.440
A true beauty keeps her lips natural.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.480
Ji Ling selection, I say.

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:53.550
This is exactly the style.

00:08:53.750 --> 00:08:55.270
You've already dressed up this much.

00:08:55.270 --> 00:08:56.360
Bear with it a little.

00:09:07.390 --> 00:09:08.230
Just as I thought.

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:09.510
Someone once said,

00:09:09.510 --> 00:09:11.030
fine clothes make the man.

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.600
Even the cold-hearted Demon Sovereign

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:15.790
may one day become a charming gentleman.

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:19.680
See for yourself.

00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:27.480
Still lacking something.

00:09:31.750 --> 00:09:32.590
Open your mouth.

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:38.790
I'm really good at it.

00:09:42.620 --> 00:09:46.460
(Hot Spring Pavilion)

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:53.910
Where's the wine?

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:55.080
Pour me a drink.

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:56.750
That nearly choked me.

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.280
Your Grace,

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:03.840
you are a honorable demon.

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:05.670
You must never lose.

00:10:05.910 --> 00:10:06.790
For today's occasion,

00:10:07.030 --> 00:10:08.670
I worked hard to make it happen.

00:10:08.910 --> 00:10:10.200
A mere imitation

00:10:10.390 --> 00:10:11.870
dares to be compared with me?

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.000
An imitation?

00:10:13.670 --> 00:10:14.510
I…

00:10:16.750 --> 00:10:17.870
Yes, yes, of course.

00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:19.150
Your Grace, you're right.

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:22.840
They can't be measured against you.

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:33.270
Loyal and brave

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.790
with fine bearing,

00:10:35.270 --> 00:10:38.550
you're blessed by the celestial deity.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:41.360
Today is the first selection of Ji Ling.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:42.910
Now, let us welcome

00:10:42.910 --> 00:10:43.840
gentlemen.

00:10:45.030 --> 00:10:46.270
Those not involved,

00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:47.390
please step outside for now.

00:10:48.150 --> 00:10:49.030
Yes.

00:10:51.870 --> 00:10:53.150
It's all up to you, Your Grace.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:57.440
Gentlemen, you may rise.

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:25.960
Let's begin.

00:11:26.870 --> 00:11:28.150
Miss, try grilled skewers.

00:11:28.750 --> 00:11:30.550
Everything we offer is freshly made.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:34.670
Hope Jie Chuan passes the first round.

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:36.960
Then we can blend in with the crowd

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:39.120
and rescue Master.

00:11:43.550 --> 00:11:44.630
Ah, young lady.

00:11:44.870 --> 00:11:46.270
Our humble shop is more effective

00:11:46.270 --> 00:11:47.390
than Feng Tian and Jie Chuan.

00:11:47.390 --> 00:11:48.510
We answer every request.

00:11:48.510 --> 00:11:49.440
Come, take a look.

00:11:50.060 --> 00:11:52.660
(Every Request Is Answered)

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.440
Please.

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:01.710
Come here.

00:12:08.870 --> 00:12:09.870
I'll take this sachet.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.360
Five copper coins.

00:12:13.870 --> 00:12:15.910
Your stall sure charges boldly.

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:19.670
What's your wish?

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:21.030
You've passed the test?

00:12:21.790 --> 00:12:23.790
So you made a wish just for this?

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:26.440
I only feared that Lady Serpent

00:12:26.440 --> 00:12:27.550
might turn you away.

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:28.870
That's why I resorted to this.

00:12:30.870 --> 00:12:32.150
Wish for something else.

00:12:32.790 --> 00:12:33.630
You really passed.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:36.550
They're merely a group of mortals.

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:38.080
How can they challenge me?

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.610
Yes, yes.

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.200
As expected, Your Grace.

00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:42.120
You're handsome,

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:43.080
kind, and approachable.

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:46.390
That's pleasant to hear.

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:49.600
Consider this sachet as my gift to you.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:50.920
Make your wish.

00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:06.900
(May)

00:13:15.420 --> 00:13:18.780
(May)

00:13:32.630 --> 00:13:33.790
Just tossing a sachet.

00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:34.800
Is that necessary?

00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:36.080
You don't understand.

00:13:36.750 --> 00:13:38.870
The higher I throw,
the more likely it comes true.

00:13:39.790 --> 00:13:42.000
Didn't expect the Immortal Clan
to believe in this too.

00:13:44.390 --> 00:13:45.230
Let me help you.

00:13:53.790 --> 00:13:54.630
It's gone.

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:56.240
The higher it flies,

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:57.360
the stronger the wish.

00:13:58.030 --> 00:13:58.960
Your wish now

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.030
has reached the skies.

00:14:00.670 --> 00:14:02.870
Even Feng Tian might spot it.

00:14:03.030 --> 00:14:04.000
Cannot let that happen.

00:14:04.240 --> 00:14:05.270
My wish

00:14:05.510 --> 00:14:07.120
must be kept from Immortal Feng Tian

00:14:07.630 --> 00:14:09.030
and even more so from my master.

00:14:24.200 --> 00:14:25.120
(May)

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:28.080
(the immortals and demons
never wage war.)

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:48.200
Lofty ambition reaches to the sky.

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:52.150
Blessings endure,
bringing honor to the clan.

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.720
This glazed fish tank

00:14:54.030 --> 00:14:55.480
belongs to Lady Serpent Immortal.

00:14:55.590 --> 00:14:58.080
She brought it down from the Heaven.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:01.080
Whoever can make the koi
sink to the bottom

00:15:01.510 --> 00:15:03.470
shall be entitled Chief of Ji Ling.

00:15:03.660 --> 00:15:06.150
Tomorrow, he shall wed Lady Serpent.

00:15:06.750 --> 00:15:07.630
Now,

00:15:07.630 --> 00:15:10.000
let us welcome the first gentleman.

00:15:40.600 --> 00:15:41.440
Ji Li.

00:15:42.080 --> 00:15:42.920
Ji Li.

00:15:43.790 --> 00:15:44.840
Your fish scales...

00:15:54.750 --> 00:15:56.030
This pendant is formed from

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:57.200
my Demonic Ether.

00:15:57.840 --> 00:15:59.600
Keep it close and nurture it

00:16:00.270 --> 00:16:02.080
and the scales will not appear.

00:16:04.790 --> 00:16:05.910
Why are you staring off?

00:16:07.910 --> 00:16:08.750
I…

00:16:15.200 --> 00:16:16.630
I'm just thinking of a solution.

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:19.120
How do we get that fish to sink?

00:16:20.440 --> 00:16:21.510
I have my own way.

00:16:22.750 --> 00:16:23.790
Demonize it,

00:16:24.630 --> 00:16:25.790
and it will sink without fail.

00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:27.670
This is the Mortal Realm.

00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:28.550
Great Demon,

00:16:28.720 --> 00:16:29.910
what are you talking about?

00:16:31.790 --> 00:16:33.000
I have my own way

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:34.840
to make this little fish sink.

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:01.550
- How could he...?
- Right.

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:02.920
Switch the fish.

00:17:03.320 --> 00:17:04.240
Failed.

00:17:06.490 --> 00:17:07.480
Let's welcome

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:09.070
the next gentleman.

00:17:14.830 --> 00:17:16.830
Two or three inches of red carp.

00:17:17.160 --> 00:17:18.960
Seven or eight stalks of white lotus.

00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:20.920
Today, I'm here for the selection.

00:17:21.480 --> 00:17:23.750
Big fish bring more blessings.

00:17:32.880 --> 00:17:33.750
Switch the fish.

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:34.590
Failed.

00:17:35.160 --> 00:17:37.590
Let us welcome the next gentleman.

00:17:54.640 --> 00:17:55.480
Jie Chuan.

00:17:56.350 --> 00:17:57.310
Jie Chuan.

00:17:57.310 --> 00:17:58.590
Great Demon,

00:18:00.830 --> 00:18:01.720
I am Ji Li.

00:18:02.720 --> 00:18:03.560
Let me.

